@startuml
title Departmental Lending Request Rescheduling

|User|
start
:Open lending request form;
:Select item and needed date;
:Submit request;

|System|
:Check request submission time;
:Check request window rules;

if (Request is at least 24 hours in advance\nand within allowed request period?) then (Yes)
  :Register request for selected date;
  :Notify user of submitted request;
else (No)
  :Determine next valid lending date;
  :Move request to next eligible day;
  :Notify user of rescheduled request date;
endif

end
@enduml